{
  "title": "Xtra Creamy Uruguayan Fish Stir Fry",
  "description": "A pescatarian friendly Uruguayan dish featuring mayonnaise and stir fried fish, this recipe is a must try for anyone looking for a creamy and indulgent meal. It has a nice balance of mustardy and creamy flavors.",
  "cuisine": "Uruguayan",
